613
00:42:34,390 --> 00:42:36,116
Christopher!

614
00:42:36,117 --> 00:42:38,074
Nama saya Kristoff!

615
00:42:41,938 --> 00:42:43,819
Tunduk!

616
00:42:47,442 --> 00:42:50,145
- Awak hampir bakar saya!
- Tapi tidak, kan?

617
00:42:56,491 --> 00:42:57,863
Sedia untuk melompat, Sven!

618
00:42:57,864 --> 00:43:00,034
Awak tak boleh arahkan dia.

619
00:43:00,075 --> 00:43:03,696
Tapi saya! Lompat, Sven!

